snippet.title: Super Farm PS2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Playing as some different animals in 3 areans fetching fish for Pamela, touching Pamela and a fight to grab the most teeth.
I use a Elgato Game Capture for recording.

If you liked this gameplay, check out other gameplay videos here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHFxgM0XqVksRlERH4coypoXhgDUQipzJ
